        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/355/436",
        "text": [
          "۳۵۵. وَبَنَى رَجُلٌ مِنْ عُمَّالِهِ بِنَاءً فَخْماً فَقَالَ (عليه السلام):"
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "355. One of the officers of Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, built a stately house, about which Amīr al-mu’minīn said:"
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 2207,
        "local_index": 2,
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:3:438:2",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/355/437",
        "text": [
          "أَطْلَعَتِ الْوَرِقُ رُؤُوسَهَا! إِنَّ الْبِنَاءَ يَصِفُ لَكَ الْغِنَى."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "This is silver coins showing forth their faces. Certainly, this house speaks of your riches."
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
